      "comment_id" : 40054167,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "I would suggest: <code>if (SystemUtils.IS_JAVA_1_5) { &#47;* 1.5 specific code *&#47; } else if (SystemUtils.isJavaVersionAtLeast(1.6f)) { &#47;* modern code *&#47; } else { &#47;* fall back to legacy code *&#47; }</code>. Specific code above, generic code below, fallback code at the very bottom."
