      "comment_id" : 42186938,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "@ADTC: You are right. Your structure is better than mine. But the reason I want to keep my structure is because people can see that <code>SystemUtils.JAVA_VERSION_FLOAT</code> can and/or must be compared with a float literal. That&#39;s my only excuse :)"
