    "creation_date" : 1400291982,
    "answer_id" : 23706899,
    "question_id" : 2591083,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Example for Apache Commons Lang:</p>\n\n<pre><code>import org.apache.commons.lang.SystemUtils;\n\n    Float version = SystemUtils.JAVA_VERSION_FLOAT;\n\n    if (version &lt; 1.4f) { \n        // legacy\n    } else if (SystemUtils.IS_JAVA_1_5) {\n        // 1.5 specific code\n    } else if (SystemUtils.isJavaVersionAtLeast(1.6f)) {\n        // 1.6 compatible code\n    } else {\n        // dodgy clause to catch 1.4 :)\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
