    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<h1><code>Runtime.version()</code></h1>\n<p>Since Java 9, you can use <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/12/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/Runtime.html#version()\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>Runtime.version()</code></a>, which returns a <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/12/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/Runtime.Version.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>Runtime.Version</code></a>:</p>\n<pre><code>Runtime.Version version = Runtime.version();\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
