    "answer_id" : 46377995,
    "question_id" : 2591083,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just a note that in Java 9 and above, the naming convention is different. <code>System.getProperty(\"java.version\")</code> returns <code>\"9\"</code> rather than <code>\"1.9\"</code>.</p>\n"
