    "answer_id" : 46891599,
    "question_id" : 2591083,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you can have dependency to apache utils you can use org.apache.commons.lang3.SystemUtils.</p>\n\n<pre><code>    System.out.println(\"Is Java version at least 1.8: \" + SystemUtils.isJavaVersionAtLeast(JavaVersion.JAVA_1_8));\n</code></pre>\n"
