    "question_id" : 2591083,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Here is the answer from @mvanle, converted to Scala:\n<code>\nscala&gt; val Array(javaVerPrefix, javaVerMajor, javaVerMinor, _, _) = System.getProperty(\"java.runtime.version\").split(\"\\\\.|_|-b\")\njavaVerPrefix: String = 1\njavaVerMajor: String = 8\njavaVerMinor: String = 0\n</code></p>\n"
  }, {
